&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Earnest empowers ambitious professionals to make confident financial decisions and build the life they envision.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Earnies are committed to helping borrowers move forward with confidence by offering smarter borrowing options with a clearer path to taking control of their debt. If you’re as passionate as we are about our mission, read more below, and let’s build something great together.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lifecycle Marketing Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; will report to&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; VP, Performance Marketing.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As the &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Lifecycle Marketing Manager, &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own Lifecycle Strategy &amp;amp; Execution: Set the roadmap and execute hands-on campaigns across a meaningful portion of the customer journey to directly drive loan volume, LTV, retention, and cross-sell.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive Data-Backed Targeting &amp;amp; Creative: Establish a sharp POV on audience segmentation using behavioral and real-time data, partnering closely with Creative to push boundaries and turn opinions into evidence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the Testing Agenda: Independently design, size, and analyze rigorous A/B and multivariate tests to maximize impact and continuously optimize campaign performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scale Cross-Product Growth: Build and scale the strategic programs that seamlessly move customers across the product portfolio (e.g., student loan refinancing to personal loans) to increase lifetime value.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner &amp;amp; Influence Cross-Functionally: Lead across the organization by partnering seamlessly with Data Science, Product, Creative, and Legal to build robust measurement models (incrementality, attribution) and ship flawlessly at speed.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic &amp;amp; Analytical Experience: 6+ years of marketing experience with a highly analytical mindset; specific channel background matters less than your ability to connect programs to business outcomes, forecast, and master the tech stack quickly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Quantitative Foundation: A degree in economics, engineering, statistics, math (or equivalent experience) that proves you naturally think in numbers, build your own reporting, and understand the nuances of attribution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Data-Driven &amp;amp; Experiment-Led: A proven track record of living in a &quot;test-and-learn&quot; environment—expertly handling hypotheses, sample sizes, honest data reads, and swift optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong POV &amp;amp; Influence: Ability to form a sharp, evidence-backed perspective on audience, creative, messaging, and timing, with the communication skills to influence senior stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactive &amp;amp; Hands-On Execution: A deeply proactive operator who takes extreme ownership of the work, manages shifting priorities, builds campaigns hands-on, and sweats the details others overlook.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Even Better:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Industry Experience: Proven track record in fintech, lending, or another regulated B2C category, including a solid understanding of compliance (CAN-SPAM, TCPA, CCPA/CPRA).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical Skills: Strong SQL skills to pull your own data cuts, paired with hands-on experience utilizing lifecycle marketing tools (Braze experience is a major plus).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced Measurement: Direct exposure to sophisticated measurement methodologies,

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Earnest empowers ambitious professionals to make confident financial decisions and build the life they envision.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Earnies are committed to helping borrowers move forward with confidence by offering smarter borrowing options with a clearer path to taking control of their debt. If you’re as passionate as we are about our mission, read more below, and let’s build something great together.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Business Operations Manager&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; will report to&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; the VP, Head of Lending.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As the Senior Business Operations Manager, you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Drive cross-functional alignment and execution across our lending business units, serving as the core connective tissue between business leaders and Product, Marketing, Risk, Finance, and Data Analytics.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Conduct high-leverage analytical deep dives and advanced financial modeling to identify performance drivers, run scenario analyses, and guide executive decision-making.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Own and maintain the quality of critical corporate operating cadences, including weekly business reviews, monthly business reviews, and board material preparation.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Coordinate annual corporate and strategic planning processes, managing cross-functional timelines, inputs, and deliverables.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Act as a versatile internal consultant, shifting smoothly across portfolio management, deep analytics, and operational tracking as organizational priorities scale.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Build a long-term foundation toward a general management track within Earnest’s lending business units.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About You:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Recent MBA graduate, or equivalent relevant professional experience in strategic finance, investment banking, corporate strategy, or financial services.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Exceptional financial modeling and analytical capabilities, with a proven ability to autonomously build scenarios and translate complex data sets into strategic recommendations.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;A high-ownership self-starter who thrives when operating without a fixed lane and feels energized by fast-paced, ambiguous environments.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Outstanding relationship-building and communication skills, with a track record of effectively influencing cross-functional teams and executive stakeholders without direct authority.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Earnest empowers ambitious professionals to make confident financial decisions and build the life they envision.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Earnies are committed to helping borrowers move forward with confidence by offering smarter borrowing options with a clearer path to taking control of their debt. If you’re as passionate as we are about our mission, read more below, and let’s build something great together.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Senior Fraud Strategy Analyst will report to Senior Manager, Fraud Strategy.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;99&quot; data-end=&quot;247&quot;&gt;You will help build and scale fraud strategy for a growing lending business—owning execution today while shaping the long-term approach as we scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 data-section-id=&quot;187pcd9&quot; data-start=&quot;254&quot; data-end=&quot;276&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;258&quot; data-end=&quot;276&quot;&gt;What You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;278&quot; data-end=&quot;984&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;bjyzqz&quot; data-start=&quot;278&quot; data-end=&quot;381&quot;&gt;Reduce fraud loss while supporting growth by building and optimizing fraud rules and strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;8f3xsp&quot; data-start=&quot;382&quot; data-end=&quot;490&quot;&gt;Own fraud monitoring and analysis, identifying risks across channels, segments, and customer cohorts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1iu0dpm&quot; data-start=&quot;491&quot; data-end=&quot;587&quot;&gt;Turn data into action by investigating trends, surfacing insights, and driving decisions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ln1d0&quot; data-start=&quot;588&quot; data-end=&quot;691&quot;&gt;Scale fraud operations by creating repeatable frameworks and improving coverage as volume grows&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1yb96n9&quot; data-start=&quot;692&quot; data-end=&quot;794&quot;&gt;Design and evaluate experiments to balance fraud risk, approval rates, and customer experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1s35zta&quot; data-start=&quot;795&quot; data-end=&quot;895&quot;&gt;Partner cross-functionally to implement fraud controls across product, risk, and engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;12gg5gq&quot; data-start=&quot;896&quot; data-end=&quot;984&quot;&gt;Support new products and channels by ensuring fraud risk is managed from day one&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4 data-section-id=&quot;v9zrqg&quot; data-start=&quot;991&quot; data-end=&quot;1008&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;995&quot; data-end=&quot;1008&quot;&gt;About You&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;1010&quot; data-end=&quot;1479&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;18sfbtx&quot; data-start=&quot;1010&quot; data-end=&quot;1098&quot;&gt;4+ years in fraud, risk, or analytics in fintech, lending, or financial services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1rzkbwd&quot; data-start=&quot;1099&quot; data-end=&quot;1163&quot;&gt;Strong SQL skills and comfort working hands-on with data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with fraud types (synthetic ID, ATO, first-party fraud)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ep9zun&quot; data-start=&quot;1164&quot; data-end=&quot;1250&quot;&gt;Experience with fraud strategy, monitoring, or detection (not just operations)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;2jruqf&quot; data-start=&quot;1251&quot; data-end=&quot;1337&quot;&gt;Ability to connect analysis to business outcomes (loss, conversion, approvals)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;kd3f3t&quot; data-start=&quot;1338&quot; data-end=&quot;1406&quot;&gt;Comfortable operating in ambiguous, fast-moving environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1kyy8sn&quot; data-start=&quot;1407&quot; data-end=&quot

&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Earnest empowers ambitious professionals to make confident financial decisions and build the life they envision.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Earnies are committed to helping borrowers move forward with confidence by offering smarter borrowing options with a clearer path to taking control of their debt. If you’re as passionate as we are about our mission, read more below, and let’s build something great together.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Manager,&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Finance (Personal Loans)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; will report to the &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Head of FP&amp;amp;A and Strategic Finance.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;As the &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Senior Manager,&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Strategic Finance (Personal Loans), &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;you will:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own financial strategy and partner with senior leaders across Product, Marketing, Operations, Pricing, and Risk to drive business outcomes and performance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead end-to-end financial modeling, forecasting, and scenario planning for high-impact initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex financial and operational data into clear, actionable insights for executive decision-making&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and refine driver-based models to evaluate ROI, pricing, profitability, and growth strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver executive-ready reporting, dashboards, and presentations to influence strategic direction&lt;/li&gt;
